Install
~~~~~~~
sudo apt-get install ffmpeg
sudo apt-get install libhtml-template-perl
sudo apt-get install apache2

cd ./bin
Expand and Install bbgallery-1.2.0.tar.bz2
mkdir /var/www/bin
cp ./flash/*  
Create /var/www/bin
cp flash/* /var/www/bin/

Generate HTML files
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Create a root album directory under /var/www/'root album'

Under the root album, create chapter album
/var/www/ 'root album' / 'chapter album'

Place photo and/or video under 'chapter album'

cp configure Makefile.in to /var/www/'root album'

cd /var/www/'root album'

# Web pages are generated here
./configure
make
make install

# From the browser...
http://127.0.0.1/'root album'/

